{"title":"北京三月好春光","authors":["臧克家"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":4,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京三月好春光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"臧克家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一辆一辆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像春天溪水流淌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜帖儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一张一张，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贴在车子透明的面上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看哪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个一个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸前佩着自己的小像，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成队成行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏上了几十层石阶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进入了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会场广阔的胸膛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彼此肩并肩，打招呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朵朵笑花在腮边开放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群众，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成百上千，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走在大街上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"停住脚步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向车队投出了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲切而又崇敬的目光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三月春光好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这春光不寻常。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国的眼光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界的眼光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐注向，注向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"崇高的人民大会堂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的使者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在尽情地端详"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亿万人心描绘的春山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对她的妩媚啧啧赞赏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夸说着，议论着，指点着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一跃而起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兴奋异常；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声音细微，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也无法把兴头掩藏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是这样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们将是个什么模样？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的雄心很大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的目标高上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撑竿一跳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请看中华健儿的力量！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冷眼向洋看世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给那些希望我们跌落的人们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个大大的失望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚强的砥柱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶得住排空的浊浪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们理想的花朵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正含苞待放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着，向着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"廿一世纪的朝阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１９９１年３月２７日＊"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}